  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dad\u0daf \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Heavy rains in four provinces",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, Uva, East, North and North Central provinces will experience rain or thunder in the evening in the coming days.",
        "A spokesperson of the department said that favorable atmospheric conditions are being created for rains in those provinces.",
        "The spokesman mentioned that there will be several periods of rain in the Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-Western provinces, Kandy, Nuwara Eliya, Galle and Matara districts today (29) and in the rest of the island there will be scattered showers or thunderstorms in the evening or at night.",
        "He also said that some places in Uva, Eastern, North Central and Northern provinces will experience heavy rains of more than 75 mm.",
        "The Department of Meteorology advises people to take action to avoid accidents as lightning accidents and temporary strong winds are also possible along with thunderstorms."
      ],
